des:
NATIVE RADIO will air live talk – shows, lifestyle and entertainment programs as well as diversified music that cuts across all different culture and genre to satisfy the choice of international listeners from across the United Kingdom and other parts of the world via our mobile app. Our business goal is to become one of the leading Online Radio stations in the United Kingdom.
Our members are going to be selected from a pool of talented and highly creative On-Air Personalities, Broadcasters and Media Experts as we aim at collaborating with fresh local and international students and graduates who have love for radio entertainment.
